
## Git sync (auto-push to GitHub)

After session end (after projects-index + Log updates), ask user:
"Pushnout změny na GitHub? [yes/no]"

If yes, run:
```bash
cd ~/Claude-shared
git add .
git commit -m "session $(date +%Y-%m-%d): <brief summary>"
git push
```

Confirm with user before pushing if `git status` shows >5 changed files.
